    "updated_at": "2012-03-31T06:14:41Z",
    "body": "Re: getting rid of naive mods, I thought about this but thought maybe having the symbols scoped to a module is useful since it gives you an item to hang the library name off of. Maybe that doesn't matter as much as I think, though.\n\n(also saves you writing extern over and over)\n",
