    "body": "@pcwalton I suppose we could do that, yes. In general we haven't any support for item-qualifier blocks yet (eg. `extern` blocks, `pub` / `priv` blocks, `unsafe` blocks for globals as in #553) but I'm not opposed to that approach. It'll take a bit of legwork, is all.\n\nLibrary names on arbitrary modules will probably come to pass as part of #2176, though I am not sure. Lots of interdependencies in this cluster of bugs, sadly.\n",
